00:07:33.340 --> 00:07:37.160
And this was true throughout
the next several decades.

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:41.730
And we still don't have a
federal anti-lynching bill,

00:07:41.730 --> 00:07:48.630
though fortunately we either don't
have lynchings since the 1950s

00:07:48.630 --> 00:07:52.200
