states that grow corn,

00:15:40.960 --> 00:15:45.760
although they have a very small
percentage of the population,

00:15:45.760 --> 00:15:50.280
have significant power
in the Senate.

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:56.290
And because the agriculture
industry is what most senators --

00:15:56.290 --> 00:15:58.220
