or Republicans,

00:15:58.220 --> 00:16:00.300
it really doesn't matter.

00:16:00.300 --> 00:16:04.350
It's -- they're representing
their constituents faithfully

00:16:04.350 --> 00:16:06.220
and honestly.

00:16:06.220 --> 00:16:10.410
They're sent to Washington
to get federal funds

00:16:10.410 --> 00:16:15.060
for local agricultural
interests including corn.

00:16:15.060 --> 00:16:21.630
So the Senate is a tribute to what
we would call malapportionment.

00:16:21.630 --> 00:16:25.450
We like to think that we believe
in the principle one person,

00:16:25.450 --> 00:16:26.940
one vote in this country.

00:16:26.940 --> 00:16:32.970 position:56%
We don't. And the Senate is the
best example and it has consequences

00:16:32.970 --> 00:16:40.170
as revealed in how it is we spend
so much money on encouraging people

00:16:40.170 --> 00:16:42.810
to grow corn and corn syrup.

00:16:42.810 --> 00:16:44.110
